</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><b>1842, March 1 - <i><a href="/wiki/Times_and_Seasons" title="Times and Seasons">Times and Seasons</a></i>, as part of the <a href="/wiki/Wentworth_letter" title="Wentworth letter">Wentworth letter</a></b><sup id="cite_ref-144" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-144">&#91;144&#93;</a></sup>
