<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEShipps19858-42"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEShipps19858_42-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFShipps1985">Shipps (1985)</a>, p.&#160;8.</span>
