<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEVogel2000443–44-69"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEVogel2000443–44_69-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFVogel2000">Vogel (2000)</a>, pp.&#160;443–44.</span>
