<li id="cite_note-99"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-99">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">See the full text of the <i><a href="/wiki/Messenger_and_Advocate" title="Messenger and Advocate">Messenger and Advocate</a></i> from December 1834, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.centerplace.org/history/ma/v1n03.htm#42">page 42</a><sup class="noprint Inline-Template" style="white-space:nowrap;">&#91;<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Reliable_sources" title="Wikipedia:Reliable sources"><span title="The material near this tag may rely on an unreliable source. (April 2012)">unreliable source?</span></a></i>&#93;</sup> and January 1835, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.centerplace.org/history/ma/v1n05.htm#78pages">78-79</a>.</span>
