<ul><li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFAllen2004" class="citation cs2"><a href="/wiki/James_B._Allen_(historian)" title="James B. Allen (historian)">Allen, James B.</a> (2004), <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://publications.maxwellinstitute.byu.edu/fullscreen/?pub=1458&amp;index=13">"Asked and Answered: A Response to Grant H. Palmer"</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/FARMS_Review" class="mw-redirect" title="FARMS Review">FARMS Review</a></i>, <b>16</b> (1): 235–285, <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.5406%2Ffarmsreview.16.1.0235">10.5406/farmsreview.16.1.0235</a></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=FARMS+Review&amp;rft.atitle=Asked+and+Answered%3A+A+Response+to+Grant+H.+Palmer&amp;rft.volume=16&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=235-285&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.5406%2Ffarmsreview.16.1.0235&amp;rft.aulast=Allen&amp;rft.aufirst=James+B.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fpublications.maxwellinstitute.byu.edu%2Ffullscreen%2F%3Fpub%3D1458%26index%3D13&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFirst+Vision" class="Z3988"></span>.</li>
